race.description: Tabtouch - Have You Got The Touch Maiden
race.comment: Tricky race. FARADIO (7) looks to have the most upside, though, particularly off what we saw last start over the mile at Pinjarra. The wide draw means he'll probably be back in the running, but he finished in good splits last start. This looks a very winnable race on what he produced there. VEXATIOUS ROSE (10) dropped back to the mile last start and couldn't finish off as she had been in her previous runs. Back out in trip looks ideal and she closed very impressively at this track and trip two back. Needs to turn the tables on FARADIO, but it won't be a surprise if she does. PARISH PRINCE (3) looks ready for this trip now and should give himself every chance from up on the speed. He's had a few goes now but so have the majority of this field. Among friends here but looks open to improvement out in trip. SAINTY CULLITY (2) jumps out in trip for the first time and the booking of CJP is a good push. SAUCISSON (5) can bounce back.
